| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4667 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cf3342d8-04a2-5464-9406-40ab5485c747"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
